<P1>T, p. 371, ll 2 to 11, p. 376, ll 40&ndash;45, p. 415 ll.,21&ndash;40, 423 ll. 26&ndash;41</P1></P>
<P>16. This time the Vendor disclosed the killing of Mr. Huang as an addendum to the agreement of purchase and sale because they, &ldquo;did not want any more trouble.&rdquo;
