<BLOCK3><TI>Feng Yun Shao aka Amy Washington (the Purchaser, plaintiff by counterclaim)</TI>
<P>53. The Purchaser, a 50-year-old Canadian citizen, is an entrepreneur with a Master's degree from Shanghai Communications University who immigrated to Canada with her husband and their three daughters in 2007 so their children could get a better education.
